text: Mkhululi Calana (born 19 January 1993) is a South African first-class cricketer. He was included in the Border squad for the 2016 Africa T20 Cup. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:South African cricketers Category:Border cricketers Category:Cricketers from Cape Town
